net.sf.extjwnl.dictionary.file

Class AbstractDictionaryFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.extjwnl.dictionary.file.AbstractDictionaryFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DictionaryFile, Owned
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractPrincetonDictionaryFile

    public abstract class AbstractDictionaryFile
extends Object
implements DictionaryFile
    Abstract implementation of DictionaryFile. This class should be implemented for each file naming scheme used. It is assumed that each file will be associated with both a POS and a file type.
    Author:
    John Didion (jdidion@didion.net), Aliaksandr Autayeu
